title: Inside Kim’s surprise birthday party
text:
What’s a rope access technician? 14:01 PM Rebecca Sullivan BESIDE his wicked bone structure and adorable “cool bananas” jokes, fans of The Bachelorette are obsessed with Richie’s job. Kim Kardashian’s 35th birthday: Kanye West threw her a surprise party October 22, 2015 3:13pm Low-key birthday ... Kim Kardashian. Picture: Marc Piasecki/GC Images Nadia Salemme News Corp Australia Network Share Email a friend 
IT has been a tough time for the Kardashians lately but the family have turned out to celebrate Kim’s birthday. 
The heavily pregnant reality star turned 35, couple-dressing with her husband, Kanye West, while out in Los Angeles, both wearing nude and vanilla tones. 
West took Kim out to the movies and then surprised her with a party at Cinépolis Luxury Cinemas in Westlake, where guests watched Steve Jobs , E! reports. Baby bump ... Kim and Kanye dressed alike on Kim’s 35th birthday. Picture: Splash Source: Supplied 
But missing from Kim’s birthday party were her sister, Khloe Kardashian, who is nursing her ex, Lamar Odom, through his recovery from an overdose at a Las Vegas brothel, and their reclusive brother, Rob, who is rarely seen in public. ‘Momager’ ... Kris Jenner and her boyfriend, Corey Gamble, carried gifts on their way to Kim’s party. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied 
It was a low-key celebration by Kardashian standards, in the wake of Odom’s ill-health, and came as Khloe reportedly called off finalising the former couple’s divorce . Birthday girl ... Kim and Kanye are expecting baby No. 2. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied 
But Kim’s mother Kris Jenner, along with Caitlyn Jenner, and sisters Kourtney, Kendall and Kylie all turned out for Kim’s party. Showing some skin ... Kylie Jenner and her rapper boyfriend Tyga celebrated Kim’s birthday. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied Blackout ... Kourtney has nailed breakup dressing since her split from Scott Disick. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied Party girl ... Kendall Jenner at Kim’s bash. Picture: Splash News Source: Supplied
